        |	PARSEINT OCURV ID OSQUARE Expr CSQUARE CCURV        {};

Expr : 
                Expr operations Expr %prec OPS_FTW      {}
        |	OP3 Expr %prec OPS_FTW                  {}
        |	NOT Expr %prec OPS_FTW                  {}
        |	NEW INT OSQUARE Expr CSQUARE            {}
        |	NEW BOOL OSQUARE Expr CSQUARE           {}
